# ⚡ EV Driving Efficiency Optimizer using Machine Learning

## 📖 Overview

The EV Driving Efficiency Optimizer is a Machine Learning project developed as part of an Electric Vehicle Internship. The system analyzes driving behavior such as speed, terrain conditions, and braking frequency to predict vehicle energy efficiency and provide intelligent driving recommendations.

The project demonstrates how Artificial Intelligence can be used to improve EV battery utilization, driving efficiency, and sustainable transportation.

---

## 🎯 Objectives

* Analyze EV driving behavior using Machine Learning.
* Predict vehicle energy efficiency.
* Improve battery utilization through driving recommendations.
* Demonstrate AI applications in Electric Vehicles.
* Promote energy-efficient transportation.

---

