## 📊 Dataset Features

| Feature      | Description                       |
| ------------ | --------------------------------- |
| Speed        | Vehicle Speed (km/h)              |
| Terrain_Code | 0 = Flat, 1 = Hilly, 2 = Mountain |
| Terrain_Name | Road Type                         |
| Braking      | Number of Braking Events          |
| Efficiency   | Predicted Energy Efficiency Score |

