## 🤖 Machine Learning Model

The project uses Random Forest Regression to predict EV energy efficiency based on driving conditions.

Evaluation Results:

* MAE: 2.46
* MSE: 10.16
* R² Score: 0.96

The model achieved high prediction accuracy on simulated EV driving data.

---

## ⚡ EV Industry Relevance

Electric Vehicles depend heavily on efficient energy management. Driving patterns such as excessive speed, frequent braking, and challenging terrain significantly affect battery consumption.

This project helps identify inefficient driving habits and provides recommendations that can contribute to:

* Improved battery range
* Reduced energy consumption
* Better driving efficiency
* Sustainable EV usage

